Se Chan podepsal smlou...

175
00:17:53,230 --> 00:17:56,850
Ne Se Chan, ale Se Jong.

176
00:17:56,850 --> 00:17:58,530
Jsem zmatený.

177
00:17:58,530 --> 00:18:02,810
